    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look at my slack notifications or my phone and it feels like im just watching a movie of someone else's life. i work all day, i talk to people through a screen, but i feel like i dont actually exist in any real way. like if i just stopped responding to everything... if i just disappeared... would anyone even realize i was gone or would it just be more silence?",
